text:
Correction of many characters in mime.types
Download fixed attachement (win32 version - return carriage & return).
Many programest use this file by third-patry applications.

1) Spaces before first extension replaced by TABs, for example:
   application/octet-stream bin dms lha lrf lzh so iso dmg dist distz pkg bpk dump elc deploy
2) merge duplicate mime-types:
   application/vnd.stardivision.writer sdw vor

For consideration, please provide a unified diff (diff -u) against the copy in trunk

http://svn.apache.org/viewvc/httpd/httpd/trunk/docs/conf/mime.types?view=markup

I do not think you should include the DOS line ending change.

Since I clicked through, I'll clarify that the change adds tabs where there weren't any, not de-tabbing.
